text: Noord-Beveland, Zeelandic: Noôrd-Beveland or Noord-Beveland, is a (former) island and municipality of the province of Zeeland, the Netherlands. In 2016 the municipality had about 7,400 people. The municipality covers an area of 122 km², the island an area of 86 km². == Other websites == * Category:Zeelandic Islands Category:Municipalities of Zeeland
